Symbol.Script_3D:
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_OFF then end
pen gs_cont_pen resol gs_resol
if not(gs_shadow) then shadow off
add a/2, b/2, 0
mulz zzyzx/kz muly b/kx rotz -90 addz x addx -10*x*sqr(2)/2-3*x-7*x*sqr(2)/2+kx/2
material gs_seat_mat
mulz -1 cutplane del 1 roty -45
revolve 8, 360, 2, 0, 0, 1, 10*x, 0, 901, 0, -90, 4001, 10*x, 7*x, 901, 0, -135, 4001, 2*x, 0, 301, 10*x+6*x*sqr(2)/2, 0, 901, 0, 44, 4001
cutend
del 1 addx 10*x*sqr(2)/2 addz -x roty -90 material gs_frame_mat revolve 4, 360, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 5*x, 1, x/3, 6*x, 1, x, 10*x*sqr(2)/2, 1 del 3
del 5
del 1
Symbol.Script_2D:
! ====================================================================== ! SCALE ! ======================================================================
call "2dDetailLevel" parameters gs_detlevel_2D_m = gs_detlevel_2D_m, returned_parameters det2D
!!! ******************************** 2D
pen gs_cont_pen fill gs_fill_type
unID = 1 hotspot2 a/2, b/2, unID : unID = unID + 1 hotspot2 a/2, 0, unID : unID = unID + 1 hotspot2 a/2, b, unID : unID = unID + 1
call "fa_minimalspace" parameters all MSType = 3,unID = 3000
!!! ******************************** 1/50 unID = 10 IF det2D = 3 THEN mul2 1, b/kx hotspot2 0, 3*x+7*x*sqr(2)/2, unID : unID = unID + 1 hotspot2 a, 3*x+7*x*sqr(2)/2, unID : unID = unID + 1 poly2_b 3, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, a, 3*x+7*x*sqr(2)/2, 1, a/2, 3*x+7*x*sqr(2)/2, 901, a/2, 180, 4000 del 1
k1=b/kx k2=(3*x+7*x*sqr(2)/2)*k1/(a/2) mul2 1, k2 poly2_b 3, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, (3*x+7*x*sqr(2)/2)*k1/k2, 1, a/2, (3*x+7*x*sqr(2)/2)*k1/k2, 901, 0, 180, 4000 del 1
arc2 a/2, b/2-x, 3*x, 70, 110 else hotspot2 0, b/2,unID : unID = unID + 1 hotspot2 a, b/2,unID : unID = unID + 1 k=b/a mul2 1, k poly2_b 2, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, a/2, b/2/k, 901, a/2, 360, 4001 del 1
endif
Symbol.Script_1D:
! const values for parameter: gs_detlevel_3D_m DLEV3D_OFF = 0 DLEV3D_SIMPLE = 1 DLEV3D_DETAILED = 2 DLEV3D_DRAFT = 3
x=a/20
kx=(13*x+7*x*sqr(2)/2) kz=(4*x+17*x*sqr(2)/2)
